<title>Description</title>

<para>A <tag>macrosynopsis</tag> contains the syntax summary of a
programming language macro.</para>

<para>This is one of the few places where DocBook attempts to model as
well as describe. The content model of <tag>unionsynopsis</tag> was designed
to capture a wide range of semantics.</para>

